main.java.model.priceserver

Class PriceServer

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.java.model.priceserver.PriceServer

  • public class PriceServer
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides priceserver bid/ask prices and volumes for a single instrument. Prices can be one of three: live, manual or historical One PriceServer per one instrument to be traded. So one for SPY, another one for DIA etc.
